  "title": "Detection and assay of siderophores in cowpea rhizobia (Bradyrhizobium) using radioactive Fe (59Fe)",
  "abstract": "In this paper we describe a method for the detection and assay of siderophore (catechol type) using radioactive 59Fe. Using this method we have found that cowpea rhizobia (Bradyrhizobium) differ in their ability to produce this type of siderophore.",
